title: Partners In Crime-Fred & Ro - Season 1
description:
Partners In Crime-Fred & Ro - Season 1

This powerful drama documentary covers the horrific crimes of Fred and Rose West and includes interviews with their closest relatives and victims who escaped.
From the violence of their early lives to the trial that brought them to justice, this is the full gruesome story of how Fred West first met Rose and why the couple went on to murder 12 girls and young women. In episode one, â€œWhen Fred Met Roseâ€, Fred's brother denies that Fred was sexually or physically abused by their parents or introduced to bestiality by their father. Episode two sees the couple move into Cromwell Street and start to kill for sexual thrills. An early victim, Caroline Owens, describes the horrors of her abduction, torture and rape. In the final episode, we discover how Detective Constable Hazel Savage fought to have the West's patio dug up, finally bringing their terrible crimes to light.

Ep 1 - When Fred Met Rose
Ep 2 - Fred & Rose's House Of Horrors
Ep 3 - The Last Betrayal
